title: Report: 'Stable' Odom transfers to LA hospital
text: Report: Lamar Odom ‘Opened His Eyes' 00:45 Things are looking up for Lamar Odom. The basketball player has “opened his eyes” as he continues to seek treatment at Sunrise Hospital in Las Vegas, according to Entertainment Tonight. However, TMZ is reporting that Odom’s body movement — including eye function — is involuntary. ... You Might Like
